[normal]Devolution [bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Some of the relevant rail services in the North of England also serve Scotland.  Transport Scotland has been consulted on, and supports, the outline governance model for devolved 
[normal]North
[normal] of England rail responsibilities. 
